Roblox recently updated their guidelines using the Name 'Roblox' or using their logo on any kind of Roblox experience. Roblox has strictly prohibited the name 'Roblox' or anything remotely close to it. #Roblox #Guidelines üóíÔ∏è

You can no longer publish new experiences containing "Roblox", "Blox", or similar in the title starting soon. (ETA unknown when this is implemented) 

Developers and players are upset because this means that a lot of experiences in the future are ‚Äúruined for them.‚Äù
